      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWARRA (8) has been solid in stronger maidens than this recently and will appreciate coming back a peg today. The claim of Cheung comes in handy and she has shown some versatility early in her career. Can bounce back to her best with the drop in distance. DIRECT DEBIT (3) missed narrowly two back before a 1.4L defeat when favourite at this track and trip a fortnight ago. Faithfull's booking is a good push for his chances and he should get every chance from the barrier. Ticks a few boxes and looks to have found a suitable race this time around. RULE THE REALM (2) is racing well without winning and draws a handy barrier again today. He's shown good early speed throughout and if he can dictate from the front here, he'll be hard to mow down. RACY RASCAL (4) returned in good order at York as a 30-1 pop and has moved to the Tapper barn since. Worth including on the back of that effort. LOONA DAWN (7) won't be far away.",
